  "notes": [
    "This clinical practice guideline provides comprehensive recommendations for diagnosis and treatment of primary adrenal insufficiency",
    "The short corticotropin test is established as the gold standard diagnostic tool",
    "Treatment involves replacement therapy with both glucocorticoids and mineralocorticoids",
